flowchart TD
    START([Start Ingestion Job]) --> SCAN[Scan furniture_assets/ directory]
    SCAN --> LOOP{For each image}
    
    LOOP -->|Next Image| DETECT[POST /detect<br/>Extract furniture crops]
    
    DETECT --> CROP_LOOP{For each crop}
    
    CROP_LOOP -->|Process Crop| PARALLEL[Parallel Execution via remote API]
    
    PARALLEL --> EMBED[POST /embed_b64<br/>SigLIP2 Vector]
    PARALLEL --> TAG[POST /tag_b64<br/>Qwen3-VL Taxonomy]
    
    EMBED --> NORM[Normalize 1152-d Vector]
    TAG --> SNAP[Semantic Snapper<br/>Map to allowed taxonomy]
    SNAP --> FLAT[Flatten List Metadata to CSV]
    
    NORM --> UPSERT
    FLAT --> UPSERT
    
    UPSERT[(Upsert to ChromaDB)] --> CROP_LOOP
    CROP_LOOP -->|No more crops| LOOP
    LOOP -->|No more images| END([Print Ingestion Summary])
